<p>These Terms, and our respective rights and obligations under these Terms, shall be governed by, and construed in accordance with, the laws of the State of California, without regard to conflict of law principles</p>
<h3 class="u-text-uppercase"><strong>Binding Arbitration</strong></h3>
<p>Any controversy or claim arising out of or relating to these Terms or the Sinister Blue Parts Club shall be settled by arbitration administered by the American Arbitration Association under its Commercial Arbitration Rules (including without limitation the Supplementary Procedures for Consumer-Related Disputes), and judgment on the award rendered by the arbitrator(s) may be entered in any court having jurisdiction thereof. &nbsp;Any such controversy or claim shall be arbitrated on an individual basis and shall not be consolidated with any claim or controversy of any other party. The foregoing shall not preclude us from seeking any injunctive relief in state or federal courts for protection of our intellectual property rights (including the rights of our licensors).</p>
